Corrected payload to SSO from 450 kg to 200 kg. Unless specified otherwise, most commonly used SSO is 550 km with 98 degrees inclination. Figure 2-4 on page 15 of "Falcon User's Guide" gives payload to such orbit as approximately 200 kg when launched from Kwajalein. The number will be somewhat higher from Vandenberg, but definitely not 450 kg.
